###1. net commands
*Review net command 

Effective user and group management is essential for ensuring secure access to resources, simplifying administrative tasks, and maintaining overall system integrity. 

net.exe is a suite of commands that can be used in the CLI to manage users and groups. Note: These commands will also work in PowerShell although they are not inate POSH commandlets.

